* [DONE] Implement fixed-size depth/state stack with bracket matching, depth
  ceiling, and container-type tracking (2026-03-10).
  OkJsonParser now carries a depth_stack[OKJ_MAX_DEPTH] array (OKJ_MAX_DEPTH=16)
